.TH K-3D "1" "June 2010" "K-3D Version @K3D_VERSION@" "User Commands"
.SH NAME
k3d-sl2xml \- Parses a RenderMan shader to create a meta file used by the K-3D user interface.
.SH SYNOPSIS
.B k3d-sl2xml
[\fIoptions\fR]
.SH DESCRIPTION
.TP
\fB\-h\fR, \fB\-\-help\fR
prints this help information and exits
.TP
\fB\-\-version\fR
prints program version information and exits
.PP
Note: input on stdin MUST be PREPROCESSED Shading Language source code.
Recommend you run this command with:
.IP
gcc \fB\-E\fR \fB\-P\fR \fB\-x\fR c <file> | k3d\-sl2xml
